WEBVTT

36:51.720 --> 36:53.160 line:80%
They charge such high prices,

36:53.160 --> 36:54.430 line:80%
and they poison the food on top of it!

36:54.430 --> 36:56.310 line:80%
Yesterday, a customer suddenly fell ill
in the restaurant.

36:56.310 --> 36:58.600 line:80%
The manager noticed
and thought it might be epilepsy,

36:58.600 --> 37:00.270 line:80%
so she immediately sent someone
to fetch a doctor.

37:00.270 --> 37:02.760 line:80%
The customer's family
was very grateful at first.
